      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "After spending a full day enjoying the outdoors, we went back to our B&B and explored before snuggling up by the fire in the living room to read and enjoy the peace and quiet that a crisp fall evening in-the-middle-of-nowhere Virginia has to offer."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I have fallen even more in love with Fall now. I’ve seen it in a way I never had before, and I’m surely a better person for it."
          }
        ]
